<p>Welcome <%= @resource.first_name %>!</p>

<p>Click the following button to verify your email address with Shyne:</p>

<p><%= button_to "Confirm e-mail address", "#{root_url}/#/verify/#{@token}", :method => :get %>

<p>If the link doesn't work, please copy and paste this code into the verification form: <code><%= @token %></code></p>

Thanks for using Shyne!
